   length).
   VERIFY: `grep -n "len(round_tripped\\[\"defaults\"\\]) == 14" tests/test_sw_sampler.py`

4. The end-to-end test asserts the round-tripped `signal_chain` list
   contains exactly the eight canonical stages (set equality plus
   length).
